title: Nanashi wa Ittai Dare deshou?
original_name: 名無しは一体誰でしょう?
sinopse: "There are three things that worry me in this moment. First, before I noticed, I was here. Second, I have no memory. Third, there is a girl with a knife in front of me. Who on earth am I?" A story in which mystery and memories cross each other. High-end mystery which asks the new era!
